            "description": "The project was aimed at creating a global network of ground stations for satellite data reception. The target were university / in-orbit demonstrator satellites. I was a Java developer taking care at first of the hardware abstraction layer and later on of the main scheduler, controlling all the operations of every single ground station.\n\nThe project was funded jointly by ESA, NASA and JAXA.",
